# ERROR TIPS
### Errors when using burner entities
-  Ensure that burner entities have fuel before using them. Many burner entities were found to have no fuel.
-  Ensure that burner entities are connected to the correct input/output before using them. Some burner entities were found to be waiting for source items.

### Errors when using steam engine
-  Ensure that the steam engine is connected to a boiler and a power source before using it. The steam engine was found to be not connected.

### Errors when using electricity group
-  Ensure that the electricity group is plugged into an electric network before using it. The electricity group was found to be not plugged in.

### Errors when using pipe group
-  Ensure that the pipe group is not empty before using it. Some pipe groups were found to be empty.
-  Ensure that the pipe group has a full output before using it. Some pipe groups were found to have full output.
